title: Watch: VICTON Drops Perfectly Synchronized Dance Practice Video For “Eyez Eyez”
text:
On March 14, VICTON revealed a dance practice video for their title song “Eyez Eyez.” 
Their synchronization is quite something else, and it is especially impressive when they all jump at once! 
Meanwhile, VICTON is actively promoting “Eyez Eyez” on music shows, and member Subin will appear on upcoming variety show “Idol Acting Competition – I’m an Actor” (literal title).
